\
## Overview\
**KnowledgeNest** is an online learning platform built using **Flask**, **React**, **MySQL**, and **PostgreSQL** in a **microservices architecture**.  \
It provides **authentication**, **course management**, **enrollment**, **content delivery**, and **reviews**, all connected via a **Flask API Gateway** with **CI/CD pipelines**, **observability**, and **analytics dashboards**.\
