## \uc0\u9881 \u65039  Component Responsibilities\
\
| Component | Description |\
|------------|-------------|\
| **Frontend (React)** | Provides user interface for authentication, course browsing, enrollment, and dashboards. Uses Axios to call API Gateway. Global state (auth, courses, UI) is managed via Redux Toolkit. |\
| **API Gateway (Flask)** | Central entry point routing requests to the correct microservice. Handles JWT verification, request validation, and rate limiting. |\
| **Auth Service** | Manages user registration, login, JWT token creation, password hashing, and MySQL persistence. |\
| **Course Service** | Handles course creation, content management, and enrollment logic. Uses PostgreSQL for relational course data. |\
| **Review Service** | Stores and retrieves course reviews, star ratings, and feedback. |\
| **Analytics Service** | Collects metrics from services via Prometheus, visualized using Grafana dashboards. |\
| **Message Queue (Kafka/RabbitMQ)** | Decouples services for events like \'93user enrolled\'94 or \'93course updated.\'94 |\
| **CI/CD** | GitHub Actions automates builds, Docker image pushes, and AWS Elastic Beanstalk/Kubernetes deployment. |\
\
