## \uc0\u55358 \u56809  Data Flow & Service Communication\
\
1. **Frontend** sends HTTP requests (via Axios) \uc0\u8594  **API Gateway**\
2. **API Gateway** authenticates user via JWT \uc0\u8594  routes to specific service  \
3. Services communicate via **REST APIs** or **message queue events**\
4. Each service maintains its own **database**:\
   - Auth \uc0\u8594  MySQL  \
   - Course \uc0\u8594  PostgreSQL  \
   - Review \uc0\u8594  PostgreSQL  \
5. Analytics service subscribes to message queue for event data and aggregates logs.\
