## \uc0\u9729 \u65039  Deployment Pipeline\
\
**GitHub Actions \uc0\u8594  Docker \u8594  AWS (ECS / Elastic Beanstalk)**  \
\
1. Push to `main` triggers CI/CD pipeline.  \
2. Each service builds a Docker image.  \
3. Images are pushed to **AWS ECR**.  \
4. Containers deployed via **AWS ECS/Kubernetes**.  \
5. Logs and metrics sent to **CloudWatch + Prometheus**.  \
